  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Sofosbuvir Plus Ribavirin in Japanese Adults With Chronic Genotype 2 HCV Infection</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3b, Multicenter, Open-Label Study to Investigate the Efficacy and Safety of Sofosbuvir Plus Ribavirin in Treatment-Naïve and Treatment-Experienced Japanese Subjects With Chronic Genotype 2 HCV Infection</official_title>
  <sponsors>
