  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the antiviral efficacy, safety, and tolerability of sofosbuvir (SOF)
      plus ribavirin (RBV) in Japanese participants with chronic genotype 2 hepatitis C virus (HCV)
      infection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
